}

<div id="fullPage">
    <div class="section">
        <div class="homePage" id="homePage1">
            <div class="pageContainer" id="pageContainer1">
                <h1 class="welcomeTitle">Sandi &amp; Conor</h1>
                <p class="dateSettings">
                    Saturday, 13th August 2021 <br />
                    Hidden Acres at The Grand Estate <br /> Ford City, PA
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="venue">
            <h2>The Grand Estate</h2>
            <div class="venue-img">
                <img src="~/img/the_grand_estate_wedding_photo-26.jpg" />

            </div>
            <div class="venue-blurb" id="right">
                <p>The Grand Estate at Hidden Acres is located north-west of Pittsburgh, PA - about a 45-minute drive from the city's downtown.The easiest access is by car, as there are no public transportation options.</p>
                <button>
                    <a class="myButton" target="_blank" href="https://thegrandestate.com/"> The Grand Estate </a>
                </button>
                <p>The ceremony, cocktail hour, and reception will all take place on site at the Grand Estate.</p>
                <p>For more information about how to get here, please click through below.</p>
                <button>
                    <a class="myButton" asp-area="" asp-controller="Travel" asp-action="Index">How to get here</a>
                </button>
